#### Hands On Demo

This introductory demo script uses source code from [Source Code](https://github.com/pitosalas/sinatra_examples)

##### Basic case
* Ruby 2.5
* Create directory myapp/ in a convenient spot and `cd` to it
* Set that diretory up as a git repo: `git init`
* Create the simplest possible sinatra app and run it
* Add app.rb, with just get '/' "hello world"
* Update gemfile, bundle, run ruby to demonstrate

##### Add database
* Update app.rb to full example
* Install Postgres: [Detailed Installation Guides](https://wiki.postgresql.org/wiki/Detailed_installation_guides)
* Add environment/ directory
* create migration
* rake db:migrate

